{
  "stem": "25209.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I'm sure we were-- we weren't out of the faith, but, as I said, just judging from after the war when my parents just both really disengaged, I don't know that-- Well, first of all we weren't kosher before the war, I think.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm pretty sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was-- I mean, I think that if it weren't for the war, we would've been really-- we would have remained, you know, within the community, which we didn't.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, I want to say yes because the thing that I told you about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- there were some other incidents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] If I can-- if I will-- if I think of something specific, I will let you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my feeling is yes, and something about graffiti, something about, you know, keeping away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but it could have actually been-- because in Russia there was a lot of it, so I can't really answer this with any definitiveness.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can tell you when I got a bit older-- my memories from the age of eight are quite clear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before that, it's pretty hazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you ask me about Russia, I will be much clearer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and, and, you know, we got to Russia in '39, so-- I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I just have to stay vague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, I've already mentioned that there was some kind of underground stuff happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother must have been involved too, although-- because she must have known that those people were there, and that it was dangerous because the Poles and the Germans were really very cooperating at the time.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
